<div id="services"><div id="right-content" style="margin-bottom:-10px;"> <div id="h-right"> <h2>We are privileged with the Wealth of Knowledge</h2> </div><div id="input-right"> <input id="ign" type="submit" value="Remove Ignorance!"/> </div><div id="svg-right"><div class="svg-wrap"><div class="grid3"></div><div class="grid3"><svg class="arrows"> <path class="a1" d="M0 0 L30 32 L60 0"></path><path class="a2" d="M0 20 L30 52 L60 20"></path><path class="a3" d="M0 40 L30 72 L60 40"></path></svg> </div><div class="grid3"></div></div></div></div><div id="wrapper-services"><div id="services-header-container"><div id="services-header"><div id="header-grid"><h2>services</h2></div><div id="header-brief-grid"><p>Let us start keeping all our futile things in a bag and at the end of month, entrust them to those who are actually devoid of them.<br>And the happiness that it fetches is not only satisfactory but exquisite.</p></div></div><div id="services-container"><div id="services-grid"><div class="icon png_one"></div><h2>Research</h2><p>Based on Analysis of Experiments performed by various Teams of our Voluteers, we select localities for Donations and Campaigning. View our Results.</p></div><div id="services-grid"><div class="icon png2"></div><h2>Campaigns</h2><p>We believe in dignity of all and hence normalisation. We help people understand the causes and consequences of Poverty, and increase forces against it.</p></div><div id="services-grid"><div class="icon png3"></div><h2>Build Happiness</h2><p>We believe ignorance is the only Poverty that exists. Help someone feel the warmth of things you don't need anymore. Let those things feel freshness and life again.</p></div><div id="services-grid"><div class="icon png4"></div><h2>How It Works</h2><p>We give you shortest and transparent way to reach people who need you and the clear results are delivered. We give options for helping people that you choose.</p></div></div></div><div id="wave"></div></div></div>